OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRather
OL,6,Fcloudy at times this evening with a
OL,7,Fsmall risk of a light shower. A mix of
OL,8,Fcloud and clear spells overnight.
OL,9,FTurning chilly in the countryside by
OL,10,Fdawn.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FSunny spells to start. Turning
OL,13,Fcloudier later with a chance of some
OL,14,Fheavy showers moving in from the east.
OL,15,FA little cooler than yesterday but
OL,16,Fstill warm in the sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
