OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,6,FCloudier to start on Tuesday but
OL,7,Fturning brighter. A settled end to
OL,8,FApril with lots of sunshine from
OL,9,FWednesday. Feeling warm, but nights
OL,10,Fstill on the chilly side.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
